# WO-168 Tier 1: host-mounted artifact directory
#
# This directory is bind-mounted into the container at /host-artifacts and
# receives load-bearing workflow output (git bundles, diff stats, manifests)
# BEFORE any remote push. See docs/recovery/host-artifact-recovery.md.
#
# Actual artifact subdirectories (named by WORKFLOW_RUN_ID) are gitignored —
# only this .gitkeep is tracked so the mount target exists on fresh clones.
